				\begin{document}$$^{-1}$$\end{document} during proton–proton (pp) collisions, and 158 μ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mu $$\end{document}b-1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
